room_title: Escape room "Space Escape" by Escape May in Cape May
room_description: Houston, we have a problem… a really big problem!  The space station you're on has been hit by heavy space debris causing major damage to the oxygen generation system.  You only have 60 minutes before your oxygen runs out!  Can you repair the system in time?  You’re going to need brains and an amazing crew to get out of this one!
